OL,4,G1125FFour in a Bed
OL,5,     GNeil and Jo welcome their rivals
OL,6,     Gto Cathedral 73 in Cardiff. Their
OL,7,     Gguests are wowed by the glamorous
OL,8,     Grooms, but the extra charges for
OL,9,     Gparking and breakfast prove hard
OL,10,     Gto swallow.
OL,11,G1155FFour in a Bed
OL,12,     GGolfer Raj hosts at the Leafy
OL,13,     GSuburban B&B in Hertfordshire,
OL,14,     Gwhere the house rules include
OL,15,     Gremoving your shoes at the door.
OL,16,     GNeil and Jo aren't impressed by a
OL,17,     Gsurprise visitor in their bed.
