OL,4,G1230FFour in a Bed
OL,5,     GThe final visit is to The
OL,6,     GWellington Inn in Hertfordshire,
OL,7,     Gwhere resources manager Felicity
OL,8,     GRainbow's spiritual approach to
OL,9,     Ghosting includes cleansing the
OL,10,     Grooms' auras.
OL,11,G1615FFour in a Bed
OL,12,     GMandi and Paul pride themselves
OL,13,     Gon their high standards at Oaklea
OL,14,     GBarns Guest House on Merseyside.
OL,15,     GBut Ian is puzzled by plastic-
OL,16,     Gcovered lampshades. And Mark and
OL,17,     GNatalie have a loose loo.
