OL,4,G1650FFour in a Bed
OL,5,     GDave and Sanchia host the second
OL,6,     Gvisit, at The Guest House
OL,7,     GWorsthorne in Lancashire. Their
OL,8,     Gguests are charmed by the 300-
OL,9,     Gyear-old cottage, but there are
OL,10,     Gcleanliness concerns.
OL,11,G1720FFour in a Bed
OL,12,     GAt Sleeperdorm Backpacker Hotel
OL,13,     Gin Newcastle, Ian hopes his
OL,14,     Gguests will leave their designer
OL,15,     Ggear at the door and bunk up in
OL,16,     Ghis cheap and cheerful dorms. But
OL,17,     Gthings turn sour over dinner.
