OL,4,G1750FFour in a Bed
OL,5,     GThe final visit is to The
OL,6,     GParsonage Hotel and Spa in York,
OL,7,     Gwhere Mark and Natalie hope to
OL,8,     Gimpress their guests with their
OL,9,     Gcountry manor, complete with pub,
OL,10,     Gspa and restaurant.
OL,11,G1820FFour in a Bed
OL,12,     GIt's the final day of the
OL,13,     Gcompetition and the B&Bers meet
OL,14,     Gfor the last time to find out how
OL,15,     Gmuch they've been paid. After
OL,16,     Gsome tit-for-tat feedback, the
OL,17,     Gwinner is announced.
